The,service,provides,a,geographic,information,service,GIS,for,locations,in,the,U,S,state,of,Arkansas,It,provides,simple,search,and,advanced,field,specific,search,against,a,repository,of,information,about,Arkansas,and,its,subdivisions,and,regions,Advanced,search,allows,specification,of,category,and,publisher,from,which,results,should,come,along,with,date,characteristics,of,results,to,be,included,The,basic,service,is,an,implementation,of,ArcGIS,and,supports,methods,of,that,API,within,its,namespace,In,addition,API,methods,support,basic,search,and,advanced,search,by,category,and,publisher,against,the,state,s,geographic,information,repository,A,separate,API,allows,interaction,with,the,data,viewer,incorporated,within,the,site